OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,4,Cappoint new Chief Fire Officer
OL,6,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue have
OL,7,Fappointed a new Chief Fire Officer.
OL,9,FIt comes after an exclusive ITV Wales
OL,10,Finvestigation revealed that the
OL,11,Fcurrent interim chief brought in to
OL,12,Fhead up the troubled South Wales Fire
OL,13,Fand Rescue Service is himself at the
OL,14,Fcentre of bullying allegations.
OL,16,FStuart Millington, who was an
OL,17,Fassistant chief fire officer in north
OL,18,FWales, faced an employment tribunal in
OL,19,FMay related to his time in north Wales.
