OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,4,Cappoint new Chief Fire Officer
OL,6,FHe was accused of bullying and
OL,7,Fharassing a colleague, allegations
OL,8,Fwhich he denies.
OL,10,FAir Vice-Marshal Fin Monahan OBE DFC
OL,11,FPhD will assume the role from Mr
OL,12,FMillington and comes from a career as
OL,13,Fa fast jet pilot and senior leader in
OL,14,Fthe Royal Air Force and MOD.
OL,16,FOver the last four months, ITV Cymru
OL,17,FWales has been investigating claims of
OL,18,F"toxic cultures" at the services in
OL,19,Fnorth Wales, and Mid and West Wales
OL,20,FFire and Rescue Service.
