OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,4,Cappoint new Chief Fire Officer
OL,6,FMore than 35 whistleblowers in north
OL,7,FWales told us when they complained,
OL,8,Fnothing was done.
OL,10,FAir Vice-Marshal Monahan will take up
OL,11,Fthe role of Chief Fire Officer once
OL,12,Fall the necessary background and
OL,13,Fsecurity checks have been completed.
OL,15,FIn the meantime, Stuart Millington
OL,16,Fwill continue as interim Chief Fire
OL,17,FOfficer.
