OL,6,FWhen asked whether Stuart Millington
OL,7,Fwill return to his position at North
OL,8,FWales Fire and Rescue Service once he
OL,9,Fhas completed the handover with the
OL,10,Fnew CFO, a representative said: "The
OL,11,Fposition is currently filled by a
OL,12,Ftemporary internal appointment which
OL,13,Fwill continue during his secondment".
OL,15,FResponding to the appointment a Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment spokesperson said: "We look
OL,17,Fforward to working with Air Vice
OL,18,FMarshal Monahan.
