OL,6,F"We would like to thank the
OL,7,FCommissioners for their open and
OL,8,Finclusive recruitment process which
OL,9,Finvolved staff and other stakeholders."
OL,11,FJoel James, Shadow Minister for Social
OL,12,FPartnership, said: "I'd like to
OL,13,Fwelcome the new Chief Fire Officer to
OL,14,Fhis role. I know I will be joined by
OL,15,Fresidents across South Wales in
OL,16,Fwishing him well, but there is no
OL,17,Fdoubt that there is a mountain to
OL,18,Fclimb to restore confidence in South
OL,19,FWales Fire.
