OL,6,F"As the hard work begins, he will have
OL,7,Four support in taking the force
OL,8,Fforward after a stalled start by the
OL,9,FWelsh Government's Commission."
OL,11,FMr Monahan has completed many
OL,12,Foperational tours overseas, and has
OL,13,Fled the RAF's support to civilian
OL,14,Fauthorities for the North of England,
OL,15,FSouthern Scotland and the Isle of Man
OL,16,Fincluding maintaining a 24/7 rapid
OL,17,Fresponse team and Mountain Rescue
OL,18,Fcoverage.
