OL,6,FIn a statement, Commissioner Carl
OL,7,FFoulkes, chair of the appointment
OL,8,Fpanel, explained they had broadened
OL,9,Fout the recruitment process, extending
OL,10,Fthe search outside the fire and rescue
OL,11,Fsector.
OL,13,FThe new leader is expected to "guide
OL,14,Fthe Service through the cultural and
OL,15,Forganisational changes it faces".
