OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,4,Cappoint new Chief Fire Officer
OL,6,FHe said: "All five short-listed
OL,7,Fcandidates demonstrated excellent
OL,8,Fskills and experience that met our
OL,9,Fdemanding person specification, and a
OL,10,Fcommitment to creating the right
OL,11,Fenvironment for our people, the
OL,12,FService, and the communities we serve.
OL,14,F"At the end of five days of exercises,
OL,15,Fpanels, and interviews, Fin Monahan
OL,16,Fstood out as the best and right person
OL,17,Ffor the role, and we are delighted
OL,18,Fthat he has accepted the invitation
OL,19,Fthe join and lead the Service."
