OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,4,Cappoint new Chief Fire Officer
OL,6,FWhile not a firefighter, Mr Monahan
OL,7,Fpreviously had a fire station under
OL,8,Fhis command and underwent basic
OL,9,Ffirefighting and breathing apparatus
OL,10,Ftraining. He is currently the Director
OL,11,Fof 'Defence Futures', the MOD's think
OL,12,Ftank at the Defence Academy,
OL,13,FShrivenham.
OL,15,FCommenting on his appointment, Air
OL,16,FVice-Marshal Fin Monahan said: "I am
OL,17,Fhonoured to be entrusted with this
OL,18,Fimportant role, and I'm grateful to
OL,19,Fthe staff, unions, stakeholders, and
OL,20,FCommissioners for their confidence in
OL,21,Fme.
