OL,3,CSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,4,Cappoint new Chief Fire Officer
OL,6,F"I look forward to joining the South
OL,7,FWales Fire and Rescue Service team. I
OL,8,Fwould like every staff member,
OL,9,Fregardless of their role or location,
OL,10,Fto feel proud of their work, and to
OL,11,Fjoin me and the leadership team to
OL,12,Frebuild the Service into an
OL,13,Forganisation where everyone feels
OL,14,Fwelcome, supported, and safe.
OL,16,F"That will help us build the cohesion
OL,17,Fand mutual support needed to fulfil
OL,18,Four mission of keeping the 1.5 million
OL,19,Fcitizens of South Wales safe."
